{"id": "1356884696440770600", "channel_id": "1356884696440770600", "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "content": "“很好，很好……深呼吸……”\n“再多信賴我一點，聆聽我的指引。”\n\n克萊門汀醫生手中的靈擺勻速晃動，暖爐裡柴薪劈啪作響，一陣深沉的睏意襲來…\n用催眠來實現深度睡眠？還真是個治療失眠的新奇方法。\n\n🍃 在克萊門汀引領下的夢境將何等美妙？守密人，用一個趣聞八卦來換取一次「酣眠療癒」如何~\n🍃 在評論區留下你的「趣聞八卦」分享，克萊門汀將親自為留言的守密人送上「好夢」。\n\n——◆——◆—— ◆◆◆ ——◆——◆——\n\n“Very good, very good...Take a deep breath—”\n“Trust me a little more，Listen to my guidance...”\n\nThe Pendulum in Dr. Clementine's hand swayed at a constant speed, the firewood in the stove crackled, and a deep sleepiness came over me...\nUsing hypnosis to achieve deep sleep? It's really a novel way to treat insomnia.\n\n🍃 How wonderful will the dream be under Clementine's guidance? keeper, how about exchanging an interesting gossip for a \"sound sleep therapy\"~\n🍃  Leave your \"interesting gossip\" in the comment area, and Clementine will personally send \"good dreams\" to the keeper who left the message.", "timestamp": "2025-04-02T06:55:21.330000+00:00", "thread_id": "1356884696440770600", "reactions": [{"emoji": "pray2", "emoji_id": "1356053116260454534", "count": 20}, {"emoji": "love", "emoji_id": "1356053099931897977", "count": 10}], "attachments": [{"id": "1356884696880906240", "filename": "1-logo.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 677483, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1356884696440770600/1356884696880906240/1-logo.jpg?ex=69ccc159&is=69cb6fd9&hm=7c51def9ee754cdb6e2caf8208cef681fdc1c6c7fe7946188c0954ca46dd7d9f&"}]}
